-- LeBron James Scores 45 as Heat Rout Celtics to Set Up Decider
-- B y   D e x   M c L u s k e y
-- 2012-06-08T03:08:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-08/lebron-james-scores-45-as-heat-rout-celtics-to-set-up-decider.html
LeBron James scored 45 points and had
15 rebounds as the  Miami Heat  thrashed the host Boston Celtics
98-79 to force a decisive seventh game in the National
Basketball Association Eastern Conference finals.  The series will conclude June 9 in Miami, with the victor
advancing to face the Oklahoma City Thunder in the NBA Finals.  The Thunder last night defeated the  San Antonio Spurs  to
win the Western Conference finals. Oklahoma City will host the
opening two games of the NBA Finals on June 12 and 14.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dex McLuskey at 
 dmcluskey@bloomberg.net  